NOTE.P:
When there is a limited supply of filtering facepiece respirators, employers may follow the CDC's “Strategies for Optimizing the Supply of N95 Respirators” (available at: 
https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/hcp/respirators-strategy/index.html
). Where possible, employers are encouraged to select elastomeric respirators or PAPRs instead of filtering facepiece respirators to prevent shortages and supply chain disruption.

